    "attributes": {
        "action": "Grant British citizenship to Kurdish people and acknowledge history",
        "additional_details": "We believe the UK Government should:\r\n1. Acknowledge what we consider is its historical role in contributing to Kurdish statelessness.\r\n2. Grant UK citizenship to Kurdish people as a form of reparative justice.",
        "background": "After World War I, the UK helped shape the Middle East. We consider the Treaty of Lausanne (1923) denied Kurds an independent state, and has left millions divided and stateless.",
